ell viability, design constructs with improved diffusion capabilities, and\naccurately control molecular concentrations in tissue constructs that may be\nused in studying models of development and disease or for conditioning cells to\nenhance survival after insults like ischemia or implantation into the body,\nthereby providing a framework for better understanding and exploring the\ncharacteristics of engineered tissue constructs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 21 Dec 2015 02:30:48 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-12-22"}
