 in the topology and\ncollective transport features, we explore the impact of the size of electrodes\nand local charge disorder. The results are relevant for designing the\nnanoparticle devices with improved conduction; they also highlight the\nsignificance of topological descriptions for a broader understanding of the\nnature of fluctuations at the nanoscale.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 21 Dec 2015 10:45:43 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-12-22"}
