s confine the\ncolder, most likely clumpy, medium. We discuss further the properties of the\noutflow in comparison with the lower resolution XMM-Newton data.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 21 Dec 2015 14:07:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-10-19"}
